name: Kinda Float
description:
Evil robots from space are trying to take down the CyberWebb! You will use your trusty jet pack to defeat them! New packages that include the final win level that was accidentally excluded from the original upload.

Kinda Float is a first-person bullet hell, level-based, jet-pack game. If you finish the game, you'll be rewarded with an explosive cutscene.

Created for Mini Jam 123: Web in 3 days!
